Home fires kill more people every year than all other major disasters combined, and a working smoke alarm cuts that risk in half. 

@FDNY and @RedCrossNY are bringing FREE smoke alarm installs to the Bronx on June 13. 

Sign up to get yours: https://t.co/ggHxU9wlYO https://t.co/RcNHKUlohW

